query:
SELECT sc.id, sc.pickingOrderId, po.customerOrderNumber, sc.status, sc.hasDivergence, sci.productSku, sci.productName, sci.expectedQuantity, sci.checkedQuantity, sci.divergence 
FROM stage_checks sc 
JOIN picking_orders po ON sc.pickingOrderId = po.id 
LEFT JOIN stage_check_items sci ON sc.id = sci.stageCheckId 
ORDER BY sc.id DESC, sci.id 
LIMIT 20;
